    base:desc "Digital twin services (e.g., the Trajectory Generator Service) send motion commands to the Physical Crane Interface, which forwards them to the Control Application and ultimately to the motor controllers over the same Python‑based communication channel, enabling the DT to command cart and hoist motions and activate the electromagnet."
