    base:desc "The overall constellation consists of the physical crane with its controllers and Arduino, a Python‑based interface layer, a set of Docker‑containerised services (DB, MQTT broker, dashboard, trajectory generator, simulator, continuous validation), and a human‑machine interface front‑end. Communication flows via MQTT and SQL, forming a tightly coupled cyber‑physical system."
