    base:desc "Inter‑component communication relies on MQTT (Eclipse Mosquitto) for signaling and command exchange, and SQL (PostgreSQL) connections for data persistence in TimescaleDB. The Physical Crane Interface uses a Python program to communicate with Arduino and motor controllers over serial/USB links."
